message.body: Hey lady! Kennedy here. Just want to make sure that the 27, 29 and 30 are on lockdown.... Getting ready to go visit my fam and wanted to send out a press release prior. Thanks so so much!
Yay, you are gonna get the most ridiculously oversized bottle of booze next time I see you! Thank you!
